      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,7 @@\n+created: 2025-12-28\n+title: Intelligent Documentation Sync\n+intro: >-\n+  This major release renames the `docs:writing` skill to `docs:authoring` to better\n+  reflect its comprehensive scope beyond prose writing. It also introduces an intelligent\n+  documentation sync hook that automatically keeps the `.docs/` repository synchronized\n+  while preventing conflicts."
